Wasu 'yan majalisar sun yi fushi da shawarar da aka yi na canja sunan su zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament, Member of the Parliament of Wales).
Wannan shawarar ta fito ne daga shirye-shiryen canja sunan majalisa a majalisar dokokin Wales.
Manyan 'yan majalisa a duk fagen siyasa suna damuwa cewa wannan zai iya zama abin ban dariya.
Wani memba na majalisar jam'iyyar Labour ya ce jam'iyyarsa ta damu da cewa za ta iya yin rima da Twp da Pwp".
