Mutane fiye da miliyan 20 sun kalli taron Brett Kavanaugh
Mutane fiye da miliyan 20 sun saurari shaidar da 'yan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh da kuma matar da ta zarge shi da aikata mugunta ta jima'i a shekarun 1980 ta nuna a tashoshin talabijin guda shida a ranar Alhamis.
A halin yanzu, an ci gaba da samun wata matsala ta siyasa, da kuma masu watsa shirye-shirye da ke dakatar da shirye-shiryen su na yau da kullum don yin wani abu na karshe a ranar Jumma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi don FBI ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda game da zargin.
Ford ya sanar da Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa cewa ta tabbata da cewa Kavanaugh ya yi ta shan giya kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin ɓoye ta a lokacin wani biki a makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh, a lokacin da ya ba da shaida mai tsanani, ya ce ya tabbata da cewa ba haka ba ne.
A ranar Jumma'a, mutane fiye da miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ta ba da rahoton sun saurari wannan jawabin.
Kamfanin yana ƙididdigar yawan masu sauraro a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a ba da waɗannan lambobin ba a nan da nan ga sauran cibiyoyin sadarwa da suka watsa su, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma Nielsen yawanci yana da wahalar lissafin masu kallo da ke kallon shirye-shiryen a ofisoshinsa.
Don yin la'akari da wannan, muna da irin wannan taron kamar na wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko na Oscar.
Fox News Channel, wadda masu sauraron ta suka yi goyon baya sosai ga naɗa Kavanaugh, ta jagoranci dukkan cibiyoyin sadarwa, da matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a lokacin sauraron da ya ɗauki tsawon yini, in ji Nielsen.
ABC ita ce cibiyar sadarwa ta biyu da ta samu masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS ta samu masu kallo miliyan 3.1 da NBC miliyan 2.94 da MSNBC miliyan 2.89 da CNN miliyan 2.52, a cewar Nielsen.
