'Yan Macedonia sun yi kuri'a a zaben raba gardama na sauya sunan kasar
A ranar Lahadi, al'ummar Makidoniya sun kada kuri'arsu a wani kuri'u kan yiwuwar sauya sunan kasar zuwa Jamhuriyar Arewacin Makidoniya, wani mataki da zai warware takaddama da ta shafe shekaru da dama da Girka da ta hana ta shiga Tarayyar Turai da NATO.
Girka, wadda take da lardin da ake kira Macedonia, ta ce sunayen maƙwabta suna da'awa a ƙasarta kuma ta haramta Macedonia shiga NATO da EU.
Gwamnatocin biyu sun cimma matsaya a watan Yuni bisa sabon sunan da aka gabatar, amma masu adawa da kishin kasa sun yi imanin cewa sauyin zai lalata asalin kabilar mutanen Macedonia da ke da rinjaye na Slavic.
Shugaban kasa Gjorge Ivanov ya ce ba zai yi zabe ba kuma yakin neman zabe ya haifar da shakku game da yiwuwar yawan jama'a ya kai matsakaicin kashi 50 cikin dari da ake bukata domin tabbatar da zaben.
Tambayar da aka yi a kan takardar zaben ta ce: "Ka amince da shiga NATO da EU da kuma amincewa da yarjejeniyar da aka yi da Girka".
Masu goyon bayan sauya sunan, ciki har da Firayim Minista Zoran Zaev, sun ce wannan shi ne farashin da za a biya domin a shigar da Macedonia cikin hukumomi kamar EU da NATO, daya daga cikin kasashen da ke tasowa tun bayan rushewar tsohuwar Yugoslavia.
"Na zo yau don in yi zabe a madadin ƙasar, don matasan Makidoniya su rayu cikin 'yanci a ƙarƙashin jagorancin Tarayyar Turai domin hakan na nufin rayuwa mai aminci ga dukanmu", in ji Olivera Georgijevska, 79, a Skopje.
Ko da yake ba shi da tilas a doka, yawancin 'yan majalisa sun ce za su yi biyayya da sakamakon zaben don su tabbatar da shi.
Canjin sunan zai bukaci rinjaye na kashi biyu bisa uku a majalisar.
Hukumar zabe ta jihar ta ce babu rahoton rashin daidaito har zuwa karfe 1:00.
Duk da haka, yawan jama'a ya kai kashi 16 cikin 100 ne kawai, idan aka kwatanta da kashi 34 cikin 100 a zaben da aka yi a 2016, lokacin da kashi 66 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a da aka yi rajista suka yi zabe.
"Na zo ne don in yi zabe ga 'ya'yana, wurinmu a Turai ne", in ji Gjose Tanevski, mai shekara 62, mai jefa kuri'a a babban birnin kasar, Skopje.
Firayim Ministan Macedonia Zoran Zaev, matarsa Zorica da ɗansu Dushko sun kada kuri'a a kan zaben raba gardama a Macedonia don sauya sunan ƙasar don buɗe ƙofar shiga NATO da Tarayyar Turai a Strumica, Macedonia, a ranar 30 ga Satumba, 2018.
A gaban majalisar dokokin kasar Skopje, Vladimir Kavardarkov, mai shekara 54, yana shirya wani karamin mataki kuma yana ajiye kujeru a gaban alfarwa da waɗanda suke son yin tir da kuri'ar raba gardama suka kafa.
