Trump zai yi magana game da sauraron da ake yi a wannan makon na dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya zama mai rikitarwa saboda zargin cin zarafin jima'i tare da an dakatar da zaben amincewa da majalisar dattijai na mako guda yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban manufar wannan taron shine taimaka wa 'yan Republican da za su yi zaben a watan Nuwamba su samu karbuwa.
Saboda haka, yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump ya ce wadannan taro biyar na mako mai zuwa suna nufin "samar da makamashi ga masu sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjayen da suke da su a Majalisar Dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai", in ji Reuters.
"Sakamakon da Majalisar ta yi yana da muhimmanci sosai ga shirinsa cewa shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu yayin da muke shiga cikin mafi yawan lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun yakin Trump ga Reuters, yana neman a bar shi a san shi.
An shirya taron a Wesbanco Arena da ke Wheeling, kuma taron da za a yi a yau zai iya jawo hankalin masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh", in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne karo na biyu a cikin wata na karshe da Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia, jihar da ya ci nasara sama da maki 40 a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na Jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke cikin jerin gwano a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo ya yi ƙoƙari ya ba shi ƙarin ƙarfi a cikin binciken ba", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Team na Amurka ya nuna ƙarfin hali don yin gwagwarmaya don ci gaba da fatan har zuwa ranar Lahadi
Bayan zaman guda uku, wasan yammacin Asabar na iya zama abin da wannan gasar ta Ryder ta bukaci.
Motar da ke motsawa a cikin kwandon yana da ra'ayi na wasanni wanda aka ƙirƙira wanda 'yan wasa suka yi imani da shi sosai kuma ba a taɓa yin irin wannan gasa ba.
To, ina motarsa za ta kasance yanzu?
Suna da maki shida a gaba kuma yanzu suna da maki hudu, don haka zan ce muna riƙe da wasu motsi, "in ji Jordan Spieth yayin da yake tafiya a ƙarshen rana.
A bayyane yake cewa Turai tana da ci gaba da maki hudu da sauran maki 12.
Amurkawa suna jin suna da iska a gefe, kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, kuma suna da dalilai da yawa na bege, ba a ƙarshe ba irin na Spieth da Justin Thomas waɗanda suka yi wasa tare duk rana kuma kowannensu yana da maki uku daga cikin hudu.
Spieth ya yi rashin tausayi daga wasan kore zuwa wasan kore kuma yana ba da misali.
Muryar murna ta kara daɗa ƙarfi yayin da wasan ya ci gaba, ta sa aka yi wani muhimmin abu don daidaita lissafin a wasa na hudu, lokacin da shi da Thomas suka yi ƙasa da maki biyu bayan biyu.
An yi ihu kamar haka a kan putt ɗin da ya sa suka ci wasan 15 a rami, wanda ya nuna cewa ya yi imani da cewa ƙungiyar Amurka ba ta fita daga gasar ba tukuna.
"Ya kamata ka damu sosai game da wasan", in ji Spieth.
Wannan shi ne duk abin da kowane dan wasan zai iya yi yanzu.
18 ramuka don yin wani batu.
'Yan wasan da suka fi Spieth da Thomas maki a cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata su ne Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, wanda ba a iya shakkarsa ba a gasar Ryder Cup.
Wannan ma'aurata masu ban mamaki amma masu ƙauna a Turai suna da hudu daga hudu kuma ba za su iya yin wani abu ba daidai ba.
"Moliwood" sun kasance kawai biyu ba su jefa wani bogey Asabar da yamma, amma sun kuma kauce wa bogey Asabar da safe, Jumma'a da yamma da kuma tara rami Jumma'a da safe.
Wannan hanyar, da kuma yadda makamashi suke gudana zuwa da kuma zuwa taron da ke cike da hayaniya, ya tabbatar da cewa su ne 'yan wasan da za su yi nasara a ranar Lahadi, kuma ba za a sami wani ɗan wasa da ya fi shahara ba daga Fleetwood ko Molinari don ya yi nasara a Turai yayin da rana ta faɗi a kan Le Golf National.
Zai fi kyau su yi aiki a lokaci guda a kan ramuka dabam dabam.
Amma har yanzu ba a yi magana game da ɗaukakar Turai ba.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi sauri don su kai ga Sergio Garcia, gwarzon wasan hudu na safe, lokacin da yake tare da Alex Noren.
