Turai ta ci gaba da cin nasara 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder
Turai za ta samu ci gaba mai ƙarfi a ranar ƙarshe ta gasar Ryder bayan ta kammala wasan hudu da na huɗu a ranar Asabar da ta yi nasara 10-6 a kan Amurka.
Matakin da Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari suka yi ya jagoranci da nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods mai wahala don kawo maki har zuwa yanzu a Le Golf National zuwa maki huɗu.
Ƙungiyar Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, a ƙoƙarin ta riƙe kofin da ta yi asara a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta yi nasara a kan tawagar Amurka da ba ta daidaita ba a wasan safe na safe, ta ci 3-1.
Amurka ta fi tsayawa a cikin hudu, ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya dawo da rashin nasara ba.
Ƙungiyar Jim Furyk na bukatar maki takwas daga wasannin da aka buga a ranar Lahadi don su ci gaba da lashe kofin.
Fleetwood shine farkon dan wasan Turai da ya ci maki hudu a jere yayin da shi da Molinari, wanda aka sani da "Molliwood" bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki sune ma'aurata na biyu da suka ci maki hudu daga farkon wasannin hudu a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun buga Woods da Patrick Reed a cikin 'yan wasan hudu, sun yi aiki mai ban mamaki don doke Woods da aka kashe da kuma dan wasan Amurka Bryson Dechambeau da har ma da 5&4.
Woods, wanda ya yi wasan biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna wasu abubuwan da suka faru amma ya yi rashin wasanni 19 daga cikin 29 a wasan hudu da hudu da bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, a lokacin hutun safiya, ya koma kusa da abokin tarayya Henrik Stenson a cikin foursomes don doke 2&1 Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka - lamba ɗaya da uku na duniya.
Amma, ba a samu nasarar da ake bukata ba a ranar da aka yi daɗi a kudu maso yammacin birnin Paris.
Wanda ya lashe gasar sau uku Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas sun kafa wa 'yan wasan Amurka maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun sami nasara mai ƙarfi 2&1 akan Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter na Spain a cikin fourballs kuma sun dawo daga baya don doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4&3 a cikin foursome, sun rasa ramukan farko biyu.
Sau biyu kawai a tarihin Ryder Cup, wani rukuni ya koma daga raguwar maki huɗu zuwa na mutum, ko da yake a matsayin mai riƙe da lambar, ƙungiyar Furyk tana buƙatar daidaitawa kawai don kare kofin.
Bayan sun kasance na biyu mafi kyau na kwanaki biyu, duk da haka, a ranar Lahadi counterattack alama ne a waje da su damar.
