Shawarwarin da ta yi sun jawo hankalin mutane aƙalla sau biyu kuma 'yan wasan SNL sun yi kamar sun ji kunya, in ji Variety, tare da wani da ya gaya wa jaridar: "A cikin ɗakin karatunsu akwai shiru mai mutuwa".
An gayyaci West a matsayin mai maye gurbin mawaƙa Ariana Grande, wanda tsohon saurayi, rapper Mac Miller ya mutu kwanaki da suka gabata.
West ya ba da mamaki ga mutane da yawa tare da yin waƙar I Love it, a cikin kwalban Perrier.
West ya samu goyon baya daga shugaban kungiyar TPUSA, Candace Turner, wanda ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa: "Ga daya daga cikin masu karfin zuciya: Godiya ga kiyayewa ga talakawa".
Amma mai gabatar da shirin Karen Hunter ta wallafa cewa West kawai "abin da yake, kuma wannan abu ne mai ban mamaki".
"Amma na zaɓi kada in ba da lada ga wani (ta hanyar sayen kiɗa ko tufafinsa ko kuma ta hanyar tallafawa sana'arsa) wanda na yi imanin yana rungumar wani ra'ayi mai banƙyama wanda yake da lahani ga al'ummarmu.
Yana da kyauta.
Kuma haka muke", in ji shi.
Kafin wasan, rapper ya sanar a shafinsa na Twitter cewa ya canza sunansa, yana cewa yanzu shi ne mutumin da aka sani da Kanye West. "
Ba shi ne mai suna na farko da ya canza sunansa ba kuma yana bin sawun Diddy, wanda aka fi sani da Puff Daddy, Puffy da P Diddy.
Wani dan wasan rapper mai suna Snoop Dogg ya kira kansa Snoop Lion kuma ba shakka, almara ta kiɗa Prince, wanda ya canza sunansa zuwa alama kuma saboda haka ya zama mai zane wanda aka sani da Prince.
