Tauraron Sword tauraruwa Kit Harington ta kai hari ga namiji mai guba
Kit Harington ya shahara sosai a matsayin mai gwagwarmaya Jon Snow a cikin jerin wasan kwaikwayo na tsakiya na tashin hankali na Gidan Waki.
Amma dan wasan mai shekara 31 ya yi jayayya da ra'ayin jarumi na macho, yana cewa irin wannan ƙasan a allon yana sa yara su gaskata cewa dole ne su kasance masu tsananin ƙarfi don a girmama su.
A wata hira da aka yi da jaridar The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce yana ganin wani abu ya faru kuma ya yi tunani game da yadda za a magance matsalar namiji mai guba a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri tauraruwar wasan kwaikwayon na Gidan Wuta mai shekaru 31, ya ce yana damuwa sosai game da wannan batun.
'Ni kaina damu, sosai a yanzu - abin da ya kasance mu kuskure da masculinity?' ya ce.
'Me muka koya wa maza yayin da suke girma dangane da matsalar da muke gani yanzu?'
Kit ta yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama wani ɓangare na ƙara yawan namiji mai guba saboda halayenta na musamman.
Ya ci gaba: 'Mecece hali kuma menene ake koyarwa?
Menene ake koyarwa a talabijin, da kuma a kan titi, da ya sa yara su yi tunanin cewa dole ne su kasance cikin wannan hanyar mutum?
Ina ganin wannan na daga cikin manyan matsalolin zamaninmu - ta yaya za mu iya canja abubuwa?
Domin akwai wani abu da ya faru da matasa.'
A lokacin hira ta kuma yarda cewa ba za ta yi wani prequel ko sequel na Gidan Wuta ba lokacin da aka kammala jerin a lokacin rani mai zuwa, yana mai cewa ya ƙare da filin yaƙi da dawakai.
Daga watan Nuwamba, Kit zai taka rawar gani a cikin sake farfadowar Sam Shepard na True West, labarin wani mai shirya fim da ɗan'uwansa, wanda mai fashi ne.
A kwanan nan, actor ya bayyana cewa ya yi tunanin cewa ya sadu da matarsa Rose ne mafi kyawun abin da ya faru da shi tare da Gidan Waki.
Na sadu da matata a lokacin wannan jerin, don haka ta ba ni wannan ma'anar iyalina na gaba, da rayuwata daga yanzu, ya bayyana.
Rose ta yi aiki da Ygritte, wanda Jon Snow ya ƙaunace shi, kuma shi ne Kit, a cikin jerin abubuwan da suka lashe Emmy.
Ma'aurata sun yi aure a watan Yuni na 2018 a gidan Leslie a Scotland.
HIV/Aids: China ta ba da rahoton karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na sababbin kamuwa da cutar
Kasar Sin ta sanar da cewa yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suke fama da waɗannan cututtuka, in ji majiyoyin lafiya.
An samu wasu sabbin mutane 40,000 a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018.
Mafi yawan sababbin cututtuka sun fito ne daga jima'i, wanda ya nuna cewa an canja yanayin da aka yi a dā.
A wasu yankunan ƙasar Sin, an riga an yi yaduwar cutar HIV sakamakon zubar da jini.
Amma adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ta HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan sifili, kamar yadda hukumomin kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin suka bayyana a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma, a shekara bayan shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da Aids a ƙasar Sin ya ƙaru da ɗaruruwan ɗari.
Yada HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An kawar da laifin gay a kasar Sin a shekara ta 1997, amma har yanzu ana nuna bambanci ga LGBT.
Domin al'adun gargajiya na ƙasar, wasu bincike sun ƙididdige cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 na maza da suke yin jima'i da wasu maza a ƙarshe suna aure mata.
Yawancin cututtuka na cututtuka suna faruwa ne saboda rashin kariya a lokacin jima'i a cikin waɗannan dangantaka.
A shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin Sin ta yi alkawarin samun damar yin amfani da magungunan HIV a duniya a matsayin wani ɓangare na ƙoƙarin da ta yi wajen magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani ma'aikaci ya yi amfani da bayanan 'yan majalisar GOP don ya gano cewa akwai wasu abubuwa masu haɗari da kuma ka'idojin ƙulla yarjejeniya.
A ranar Asabar, 'yar majalisa ta Amurka ta yi zargin cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya wallafa bayanan sirri na wasu 'yan majalisar Republican uku a shafukan Wikipedia na 'yan majalisa.
'Yan majalisar 'yan Democrat a Los Angeles sun ce masu goyon bayan ra'ayin jama'a da kuma shafukan yanar gizo na 'yancin-dama ne suka yi wannan ikirarin.
"Karyata, ƙarya da kuma ƙara ƙaryata", in ji Waters a wata sanarwa a shafin Twitter.
Bayanan da aka wallafa sun hada da adiresoshin gida da lambobin waya na Sanatocin Amurka Lindsey Graham na Carolina ta Kudu da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka daga Utah.
An wallafa wannan bayanin a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani mutum da ba a san shi ba ya fitowa daga babban birnin kasar a lokacin da wani kwamitin masana ke sauraron zargin da ake yi wa dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh na yin lalata da shi.
Wannan labarin ya faru ne bayan Sanatoci uku sun yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan tsaro kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ruwaito cewa an danganta adireshin IP da ke nuna tushen sakonnin zuwa ofishin Waters kuma sun ba da bayanin da ya shafi wani ma'aikacin Waters.
Waters ya ci gaba da cewa: "Wannan zargin da ba shi da tushe ba ƙarya ne kuma ƙarya ce ta gaske.
"Wani ma'aikaci na da aka yi wa'azi da ke da sirrinsa da kuma bayanansa a cikin haɗari sakamakon waɗannan zargin da ba gaskiya ba ne, ba shi da alhakin yin hakan.
Wannan zargin da ba shi da tushe ba ƙarya ce gaba ɗaya kuma ƙarya ce".
Bayanin Waters ya jawo karambanin zargi a kan layi daga tsohon sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House, Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙin yarda da shi yana da ban tsoro", in ji Fleischer.
"Wannan yana nufin cewa ba shi da halin zama mamba na majalisar.
Idan aka zargi wani da wani abu da bai yi ba, kada ka yi fushi.
Ba dole ba ne ya zama mai saurin fushi.
Bai kamata ya yi tambaya game da dalilin da ya sa mai gabatar da kara ya yi hakan ba.
Ya kamata ka kasance da kwanciyar hankali".
Fleischer ya yi kama da yadda Waters ya yi amfani da shi wajen sukar da 'yan Democrat suka yi wa Alkalin Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukar sun zarge shi da yin fushi sosai a lokacin sauraronsa a ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican da ke neman tsige Waters a zaben tsakiyar lokaci, ya bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafinsa na Twitter.
"Ya yi kyau idan aka tabbatar", ya wallafa.
A cikin sanarwar da ta bayar, Waters ta ce ofishinta ya sanar da hukumomin da ke da alhakin wannan lamari da kuma jami'an tsaro.
"Za mu tabbatar da cewa an fallasa wadanda suka yi hakan, ya ci gaba da cewa dole ne su yi alhakin duk wani abu da zai iya cutar da dukan ma'aikatan na".
Johnny English ya sake yin tasiri - wasan kwaikwayo na ɗan leƙen asiri tare da Rowan Atkinson mai girman gaske
Yanzu ya zama al'ada a bincika nassoshin Brexit a kowane sabon fim tare da wani ɗanɗano na Burtaniya kuma wannan yana da alama ya shafi wannan farfadowar wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English, wanda aka fara a 2003 kuma ya dawo da rai a 2011 tare da Johnny English - Sake Haifuwa.
Shin wannan baƙar magana game da yadda muke yin lalata da kanmu zai zama sabuwar damar fitarwa ga al'ummarmu?
Ko ta yaya, Johnny English mai ƙwarewa da fuskar roba da idanu daga cikin sararin samaniya ya sami lasisi don yin lalata a karo na biyu - kuma sunansa ya nuna fiye da komai cewa wannan zane ne na ban dariya wanda aka haɓaka don ƙasashen masu cinikin da ba Turanci ba.
Babu shakka, shi ne ɗan sanda mai zaman kansa wanda duk da irin wannan sha'awarsa na sha'awa, yana da ɗan Clouseau, wani ɗan Mr Bean, da kuma ɗan ɗanɗano wanda ya ba da gudummawa mai ban mamaki ga batun lokacin Gloria na bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta London 2012.
Wannan mutum ne wanda ya fara ne da matafiyi kuma mutum ne mai ban mamaki na duniya wanda Atkinson ya yi a cikin tallan talabijin da aka manta da su a Barclaycard, yana barin rikici a baya.
Akwai wasu abubuwa masu kyau a wannan sabon fitowar Johnny English.
Na ji daɗin ganin Johnny English yana zuwa jirgi mai saukar ungulu yana da kayan ƙarni na dā kuma na'urorin hawan suna ta rataye a kan kwalkwali.
Kyautar Atkinson ga wasan kwaikwayo na jiki a bayyane yake, amma ban dariya yana da ɗan ƙarami kuma yana da ban mamaki, musamman yanzu da alamun fina-finai kamar 007 da Mission Impossible yanzu suna ba da wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin kayan aiki.
Abin dariya ya fi kama da yara maimakon manya, kuma a ganina, Johnny English ba shi da ban mamaki da kuma halayyar da ta dace kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi a fina-finai masu shiru lokacin da yake taka Mr. Bean.
Abin da ya fi muhimmanci a yanzu shi ne cewa Birtaniya tana cikin haɗari.
Wani dan gwanin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin hanyar sadarwar leken asiri ta yanar gizo ta Birtaniya, yana bayyana ainihin dukkan jami'an Birtaniya a filin, abin da ya ba da mamaki ga jami'in da ke da alhakin, wani matsayi wanda Kevin Eldon ya taka rawar gani.
Wannan shi ne abin da ya sa babban firaministan da ke da girman kai da kuma damuwa ya yi farin ciki, wanda ya riga ya sha wahala daga rashin shahararren siyasa: Emma Thompson tana yin iyakar ƙoƙarinta tare da wannan mutumin kamar Teresa May amma babu wani abu da za a yi aiki a kan rubutun.
Masu ba ta shawara na leken asirin sun sanar da ita cewa an yi wa kowane ɗan leken asirin da ke aiki lahani kuma za ta bukaci ta kira wani da ya riga ya yi ritaya.
Wannan yana nufin cewa Johnny English, wanda yanzu yake aiki a matsayin darektan makaranta a wani gidan kayan gargajiya, amma kuma yana koyar da darasi a kan hanya ba bisa hukuma ba game da yadda ake zama jami'in ɓoyewa: a nan za ku iya jin daɗin wasu gag masu kyau, lokacin da English ke ba da horo na leken asiri kamar School of Rock.
An sake dawo da English a Whitehall don yin jawabi na gaggawa kuma ya haɗu da tsohon abokin aikinsa mai fama da cutar Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake buga.
Bough yanzu ya yi aure, ya auri wani kwamandan jirgin ruwa, wani matsayi na budurwa mai girma a cikin Vicki Pepperdine ya ɓata lokaci.
Saboda haka Batman da Robin na masifu ga jami'an tsaro na sarautarsa sun sake shiga aiki, don saduwa da kyakkyawar matar Olga Kurylenko, Ophelia Bulletova.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista yana cikin haɗari ya faɗa cikin hanyar mai fasaha mai ƙwarewa wanda ke da'awar cewa zai iya magance matsalolin IT na Burtaniya: Jason Volta, mai ba da labari, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
English da Bough sun fara tafiya mai ban dariya: suna yin sutura a matsayin masu hidima, suna ɗora wuta a gidan abinci na Faransa; suna haifar da jahannama ta hanyar shiga cikin jirgin ruwa mai kayatarwa na Volta kuma English ya haifar da lalata yayin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da abin rufe fuska na gaskiya don yin lalata da gidan Volta.
Hakika, an tsara dukan abubuwan da za a yi a fim don fim ɗin ƙarshe, amma duk da haka da kuma yadda ake nuna ladabi da kuma ban sha'awa, akwai wasu shirye-shiryen talabijin na yara a cikin labarin.
Duk abin da ke cikinta yana da kyau.
Kuma kamar yadda ya faru da sauran fina-finai na Johnny English, ban iya yin watsi da tunani ba: Shin masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya ba za ta iya ba Rowan Atkinson rawar da za ta yi adalci ga basirarsa ba?
Jam'iyyar Labour ta yi musun cewa tana shirin samar da shirin da zai sa 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako amma a biya su biyar
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn tana tunanin shirin da zai ba da damar 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako, duk da cewa ana biya su biyar.
Jam'iyyar ta so manyan kamfanoni su ba da kuɗin da suka samu daga juyin juya halin fasaha ta wucin gadi ga ma'aikata ta hanyar ba su ranar hutu ta musamman.
Hakan zai sa ma'aikata su yi kwana uku a karshen mako kuma su riƙa samun albashin da suka biya.
Wasu sun ce wannan ra'ayin zai dace da tsarin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar da kuma shirin da ake yi na karkatar da kasar zuwa ga ma'aikata.
Majalisar ta amince da sauye-sauyen zuwa kwana huɗu a matsayin hanya ga ma'aikata su amfana daga tattalin arzikin da ke ci gaba.
Wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa jaridar The Sunday Times cewa: An yi hasashen za a sake duba tsarin siyasa a ƙarshen wannan shekara.
Ba za a yi aiki ba, amma mako na aiki na kwana huɗu yana da burin da ya jitu da tsarin jam'iyyar na sake daidaita tattalin arzikin da ke goyon bayan ma'aikata da kuma tsarin masana'antu a matsayin dukansa.
Jam'iyyar Labour ba ita ce ta farko da ta goyi bayan irin wannan ra'ayin ba, tun da Green Party ta yi alkawarin yin aiki na kwana hudu a cikin yakin neman zaben shekara ta 2017.
Duk da haka, wannan ba shi da goyon bayan jam'iyyar Labour.
Wani kakakin jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: Babu wani aiki na kwana hudu a cikin tsarin siyasa na jam'iyyar kuma ba a tattauna batun a halin yanzu.
Shadow Chancellor John McDonnell ya yi amfani da taron 'yan majalisar 'yan Adam na makon da ya gabata don bayyana ra'ayinsa game da juyin juya halin zamantakewar tattalin arziki.
Mr McDonnell ya ce ya ƙudura niyyar sake samun iko daga 'masu gudanarwa ba tare da fuska ba' da 'masu ƙwarewa' a cikin kamfanonin gwamnati.
Shadow Chancellor's plans kuma sun nuna cewa masu hannun jari na yanzu na kamfanonin rarraba ruwa ba za su iya samun cikakken hannun jari ba, tun da gwamnatin Labour za ta iya yin 'yancin' bisa halayen da ake ganin ba daidai ba ne.
