Masana kimiyya na National Trust for Scotland za su yi nazarin jarfa da kuma ferns, da kuma 'yan kunne masu launin ruwan kasa da kuma ferns na Daubenton a Inverewe Gardens, a Wester Ross.
Za a saka na'urori na musamman a wurare masu muhimmanci a kusa da gidan don yin la'akari da ayyukan da bats suke yi a lokacin kakar.
