Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
A cewar majiyoyin hukuma, akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da tsunami da suka afkawa garin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a.
An katse sadarwa kuma jami'an agaji ba su samu wani bayani daga yankin Donggala ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da tsakiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5.
Bayan bala'in, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga Palu.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya ne, wanda ke kusa da bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi kuma yana da yawan mazauna kusan 379,800 a cikin 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka addabi birnin, yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa.
Donggala wani yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 mil) na bakin teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A shekarar 2017, yankin da ke ƙarƙashin wani lardin, ya kai kimanin mutane 299,200.
Fishing da noma sune manyan hanyoyin da ake ciyar da tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya kuma musamman yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Harkokin hakar nickel ma suna da muhimmanci a lardin, amma suna da yawa a Morowali, a bakin tekun Sulawesi.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami ya addabi Palu da Donggala sau da yawa, in ji Hukumar Kula da Rashin Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a birnin Donggala.
Wani tsunami ya afkawa yankin yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996 inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake kira Pacific Fire Belt kuma tana fama da girgizar ƙasa sau da yawa.
Ga wasu daga cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami mafi tsanani a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a gabar yamma ta lardin Aceh a arewacin Sumatra ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14 inda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa gabar yamma ta Sumatra tsakanin ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias a gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa yankin kudu na Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa gabar kudu ta Kudu inda ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afku kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, a gabashin Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani karamin girgizar kasa ya afkawa Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ya haifar da lalacewa da firgici ga mutanen da suka tuna da girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
A wannan yanayin babu tsunami amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a ƙarƙashin rushewar.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, yawancinsu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta hana dubban masu yawon bude ido zuwa wurin.
