Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa na musamman ga wadanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York
Masu gabatar da kara a jihar New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ya kai harin ta'addanci da ya kashe mutane takwas. Wannan hukuncin kisa ne da ba a taɓa yi ba tun shekara ta 1953.
An zargi Saipov, mai shekara 30, da yin amfani da wata motar haya ta Home Depot don yin amfani da ita a kan hanyar hawa ta hanyar West Side Highway a yankin Lower Manhattan ta hanyar kashe masu tafiya da kuma masu hawa keke a watan Oktoba.
A karkashin yanayin da ake bukata a yi wa hukuncin kisa a kudancin New York, don a yi hukunci a kan hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas "da gangan" kuma ya yi mummunan rauni.
A cewar takardar kotu, waɗannan masu tuhumar za su iya kai ga hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, babban kotun tarayya ta yanke hukunci a kan Saipov bisa zargin 22 da suka hada da zargin kisa guda takwas da suka shafi aikata laifi, wanda masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da shi a lokuta na aikata laifuka, da kuma zargin zalunci da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da kuma shiri", inda suka bayyana yadda Saipov ya kai harin a matsayin "m, mummunan, da kuma lalata".
Sanarwar ta farko ta ce "Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco lahani, ɓata rai da asarar rai".
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma sun shige tun lokacin da kotun kudancin New York ta kai karar kisa ta ƙarshe.
An zargi mutumin da ake tuhuma da shi, Khalid Barnes, da kisan 'yan kasuwa biyu, amma a ƙarshe an yanke masa hukuncin rai a watan Satumba na shekara ta 2009.
An yanke hukuncin kisa a New York a shekarar 1953 a kan shari'ar tarayya ta Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka zargi da yin ta'addanci ta hanyar leken asiri da kuma gabatar da su ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
Ma'aurata Rosenberg sun mutu a cikin kujera na lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cewar takardun kotun, Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, bai nuna alamar tuba ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce a gaban masu binciken ya nuna alfahari da abin da ya yi.
A cewar alƙali, Saipov ya gaya wa hukumomi cewa ya yanke shawarar kai harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa.
Ya kuma bukaci 'yan sanda su rataye tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin sa.
A kan zargin da ake masa, ya ce bai yi laifi ba.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu kare jama'a na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce "a bayyane yake ya yi takaici" da hukuncin da ake yanke wa masu gabatar da kara.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar karɓan laifi da kuma ɗaurin rai a kurkuku ba tare da wata dama ta sake ba zai ƙara wa dukan mutanen da ke cikin wannan yanayin baƙin ciki ba", in ji Patton.
A baya, rukunin masu kare Saipov sun roƙi masu gabatar da kara kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
Wani dan majalisa Tory ya ce dole ne NIGEL FARAGE ya jagoranci tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi rantsuwa a yau cewa zai "tattara sojojin jama'a" a lokacin zanga-zangar da ya yi a taron Tory.
Lokacin da wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Theresa May ya ba da shawarar cewa ya kamata ya kula da tattaunawar da Tarayyar Turai, tsohon shugaban jam'iyyar 'yancin kai ta Birtaniya ya ce 'yan siyasa su "ji matsa lamba" daga masu shakka game da kudin Tarayyar Turai.
A watan Maris, dan majalisa mai zaman kansa Peter Bone ya shaida wa Birmingham cewa Birtaniya "za ta riga ta fita daga Turai" idan Farage ya zama sakataren Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da May ke fuskanta wajen daidaita matsayin jam'iyyarta da ke da rabuwa sosai, Tories ne suka nuna cewa suna son zama a Turai kuma sun halarci zanga-zangar daban-daban na Brexit a London.
Firayim Minista yana kokarin aiwatar da shirin Chequers a tsakanin hare-haren magoya bayan Brexit, wadanda suke son su zauna a Turai da Tarayyar Turai.
'Yan ta'addan sun nace da ci gaba da ƙoƙarin cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da irin wannan mummunan ra'ayi da ake yi a kai a kai, da kuma tilasta wa masu son Euro-sceptics da 'yan Labour su zabi tsakanin abin da May ta ce da kuma "rashin tsari".
A taron da aka yi a Solihull, Bone ya ce yana son ya daina shirin Chequers.
Ya ce Farage ne ya kamata ya gudanar da tattaunawar da Brussels.
Ya ce: "Za mu riga mun fita daga Turai a wannan lokacin.
Dan majalisa mai suna Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Ina goyon bayan Brexit amma dole ne mu yi watsi da shirin Chequers".
Da yake bayyana dalilinsa na adawa da Tarayyar Turai, ya ce: "Ba mu yi yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya domin mu bauta wa Allah ba.
Muna son mu yi amfani da dokokinmu a ƙasarmu".
Bone ya yi watsi da ra'ayoyin da ke nuna cewa za a canja ra'ayin jama'a daga zaben 2016: "Tunanin cewa Birtaniya sun canza ra'ayi kuma suna son su zauna a Turai ba gaskiya ba ne".
Tory 'yar majalisa Andrea Jenkyns, mai goyon bayan Brexit, ta halarci gangamin kuma ta gaya wa manema labarai: "Na gaya wa Firayim Minista kawai ya saurari mutane.
Wannan shirin Chequers ba shi da kyau ga jama'a, kuma ba za a amince da shi ba, kuma ba za a amince da shi ba daga jam'iyyarmu da kuma 'yan jarida da ke yawo a tituna suna neman kuri'u don su ba mu damar yin zabe.
Ka manta da shirin Chequers kuma ka fara sauraro".
A cikin wata sanarwa mai zurfi ga May, ya kara da cewa: "Prime ministers na iya riƙe matsayinsu idan sun cika alkawuransu".
A taron, Farage ya ce 'yan siyasa su iya "ji matsa lamba" idan suna son su yi wa'adi game da shawarar da aka yanke a zaben 2016.
"Yanzu batun amincewa ne tsakaninmu, da al'ummarmu, da kuma jami'an siyasa", in ji shi.
"Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit kuma muna nan a yau don gaya musu cewa ba za mu yarda su yi hakan ba".
A cikin sakon da ya aika wa taron da ke farin ciki, ya kara da cewa: "Ina so ku sa 'yan siyasa su ji matsin lamba a kan mu da ke shirin cin amanar Brexit.
Muna son mu tara sojojin mutanen wannan kasar da suka yi zabe a kan Brexit kuma ba za mu tsaya ba har sai mun zama Burtaniya mai zaman kanta, mai zaman kanta, mai girman kai".
