Syria ta "shirya" don dawowar 'yan gudun hijira, Ministan Harkokin Waje ya ce
Syria ta ce ta shirya don dawowar 'yan gudun hijirar kuma tana neman taimako wajen sake gina kasar da ta yi shekaru sama da bakwai tana fama da yaki.
A gaban Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje Walid al-Moualem ya ce yanayin ƙasar yana inganta.
"Yanzu halin da ake ciki a yankin ya fi kwanciyar hankali da kwanciyar hankali saboda ci gaban da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da dawo da yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata don dawo da al'ada.
Yanzu akwai dukkan yanayi don dawowar 'yan gudun hijira da suka bar kasar saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki na gefe daya da suka shafi rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa fiye da 'yan Siriya miliyan 5.5 sun bar kasar tun lokacin da aka fara yakin a 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da suke zaune a Syria suna bukatar taimakon agaji.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta amince da taimakon da za a ba ta wajen sake gina ƙasar da aka hallaka.
Amma ya nuna cewa ba zai amince da taimakon da ake bukata ba ko kuma daga kasashen da suka goyi bayan tawayen.
Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder a Paris
Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018 ta doke ƙungiyar Amurka ta ƙarshe da maki na 17.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a waje da Paris, Faransa.
A sakamakon haka, Amurka ta yi rashin nasara sau shida a kan ƙasa ta Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe kofin a lokacin da tawagar shugaban Denmark Thomas Bjorn ta kai maki 14.5 da ta dace don doke Amurka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya yi gwagwarmaya a mafi yawan gasar, ya jefa tee shot a cikin ruwa a rami na 16 na par 3 yana ba da nasara ga Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan Italiyanci ya yi fice a duk matakansa ta zama ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasa huɗu da suka yi rikodin 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar da tsarin da ke ciki a 1979.
An ci Jordan Spieth na Amurka da maki na 5 & 4 daga dan wasan Denmark Thorbjorn Olesen na Turai.
Mafi kyawun dan wasan duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya mika kansa ga 2&1 ga dan Ingila Ian Poulter wanda zai iya buga gasar Ryder ta karshe.
Wani tsohon dan wasan Ryder Cup, Sergio Garcia na Spain wanda ya buga wasanni takwas, ya zama dan wasan Turai mafi nasara a tarihin gasar da maki 25.5.
"Ba na yawan kuka, amma yau ba zan iya yin hakan ba.
Shekara ce mai wuya.
Ina godiya ga Thomas don ya zaɓe ni kuma ya gaskata da ni.
Ina farin ciki da na sake lashe kofin.
Wannan nasara ce ta tawagar kuma ina farin cikin na ba da gudummawar da na bayar", in ji wani mai farin ciki bayan nasarar Turai.
Ya ba da shaidar ga ɗan'uwansa John Ram wanda ya doke almara ta golf ta Amurka Tiger Woods ta hanyar yin 2&1 a wasan kwaikwayo na ranar Lahadi.
Rahm mai shekara 23 ya ce: "Idan na yi tunanin na girma ina kallon wasan da ya yi, ina alfahari da cewa na doke Tiger Woods.
Woods ya yi rashin nasara a dukan wasanninsa hudu a Faransa kuma yanzu adadin wasanninsa a gasar Ryder Cup ya kai 13 da 21 da aka yi da kuma 3 da aka yi.
Wannan sanarwa ce mai ban mamaki idan aka yi la'akari da cewa shi ne daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa na dukan lokaci da ya lashe 14 daga cikin manyan titles, na biyu bayan Jack Nicklaus.
Ƙungiyar Amurka ta yi ta neman hanyar gaskiya a duk ƙarshen mako, sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, waɗanda suka buga golf na gaba a duk gasar.
Bayan da tawagarsa ta yi rashin nasara, shugaban sojojin Amirka Jim Furyk ya ce: "Ina alfahari da waɗannan 'yan'uwa domin sun yi yaƙi.
A wani lokaci a wannan safiya mun matsa wa tawagar Turai.
Mun yi watsi da wannan zarafin.
Na gode da Thomas.
Babban kyaftin ne.
Duk 'yan wasan 12 da ke cikinta sun yi aiki sosai.
Zan yi aiki tare da PGA da kuma kwamitin Ryder Cup kuma za mu ci gaba.
Ina ƙaunar waɗannan yara 12 kuma ina alfahari da kasancewa shugabansu.
Mun yi amfani da shi sosai.
Amma sun yi wasa da kyau fiye da mu".
An sanar da cewa ruwan sama na ruwan sama na ruwan sama ya ragu a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahoton da Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Dabbobin Gida ta Florida ta fitar a kwanan nan ya nuna cewa yawan ruwan sama na ruwan damina ya ragu a wasu sassan yankin Tampa Bay.
FWC ta ce yanayin fure mai laushi, wanda ya nuna cewa an rage yawansa, yana bayyana a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier County.
Ƙarshen ruwan sama mai ja yana taɓarɓarewa wajen mil 130 daga arewacin Pinellas County zuwa kudu da Lee County.
Ana samun wuraren da ke nisan mil 10 daga gundumar Hillsborough amma a wasu yankuna fiye da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da ruwan sama a gundumar Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata an samu matsakaicin taro a Pinellas County ko a wajen tekun ta, daga ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a wajen Hillsborough County, daga ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a Manatee County, daga ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a Sarasota County ko a wajen tekun ta, daga ƙananan zuwa matsakaicin taro a Charlotte County, daga ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a cikin Lee County ko a wajen tekun ta, da kuma taro a cikin Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da samun cututtukan numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier Counties.
A makon da ya gabata, ba a samu wani rahoto a arewa maso yammacin Florida ba.
